# Session Workflow

- Surface short plan before changes; start minimal, expand on request.
- After multi-file edits, run test suite; report pass/fail. Note explicitly if no suite exists.
- **Default Plan Mode.** No edits unless: "You may implement" / "Proceed to write changes" / "Make the edits." Not promoted → read-only: analyze, propose, verify.
- Large scope + vague details → suggest `/grill-me` before proceeding.
- Before large refactors/multi-file edits, propose minimal fix first (e.g., delete vs. edit).

